+# sqlcipher3 is intentionally an OPTIONAL dependency. We don't want
+# to drag in a 3 MB native wheel in dev/test environments that don't
+# need encryption. ostler_security.database already handles sqlcipher3
+# being absent gracefully (HAS_SQLCIPHER flag, falls through to plain
+# sqlite3 with a warning). For full encryption support, install with
+# `pip install ostler_security[encrypted]`.
+#
+# Migrated from pysqlcipher3 to sqlcipher3 on 2026-05-22 (Studio
